data.description: One of a kind opportunity of 3bedroom, 2 bath colonial nestled in Brookdale community. Upon entrance, large formal living room with a wood-burning fireplace. Large formal dining room conveniently adjoins the kitchen. Conveniently located just minutes from bus, train, GSP and downtown Bloomfield and Montclair. Close to Brookdale park featuring community events, concerts and cherry blossom festival.
